ActHeritage Railway Stations Protection Act
SubjectVia Rail Canada - Alterations to its railway station in Québec.
PrecisOrder authorizing VIA RAIL CANADA to undertake ALTERATIONS to interior and exterior features of its railway station located at 450 de la Gare du Palais Street, Québec, Quebec, in order to protect and preserve the heritage character of the station.
